Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.utils.game.GameObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Arrow, Goal, Character, Item, Start, Tile
public class GameObject extends Object implements IGameObject
GameObject is the base class for all game objects. It contains the position, texture, and render priority of the object. It also contains methods for loading textures and getting the size of the object. If the object wants to be rendered, it must inherit from this class.
